The Nation Online readers are tipping Miracle to win this year’s Big Brother Naija, BBNaija’s reality show tonight. Miracle is ahead of four other finalists in an online poll on our website www.thenationonlineng.net running since the beginning of the week. In the poll, readers were asked the question: Who wins the Big Brother Naija TV Show? Out of 1,703 votes as at 6.02 pm, Miracle polled 686 which is 40 percent. Tobi is a close runner up with 574 votes (34 percent) and Cee-c 245, (14 percent.) Alex so far has 140 votes, (8 percent) and Nina 58, (3 percent).